<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.7.9">
<l>aṇṭat tamararkaḷ cūḻa vattāṇi yuḷḷaṅki runtāy</l>
<l>toṇṭarkaḷ neñci luṟaivāy tūmala rāḷmaṇa vāḷā</l>
<l>uṇṭiṭ ṭulakiṉai yēḻu mōrā lilaiyil tuyil koṇṭāy</l>
<l>kaṇṭunā ṉuṉṉai yukakkak karumukaip pūccūṭṭa vārāy.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You sat there in the assembly hall</l>
<l rend="indent">surrounded by heavenly celestials.</l>
<l>You dwell in the hearts of servants.</l>
<l>Oh Bridegroom of the pure Lotus Lady!</l>
<l>You slept on a banyan leaf having consumed the 7 worlds.</l>
<l>So that I may rejoice in seeing you,</l>
<l>come so the [I can] adorn [you] with Jasmine blossoms.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
